<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-11-0443 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper defines the characteristics and function of sensors and goeson to focus on gas sensors and their main fields of application: explosionand methane monitoring, combustion control, atmosphere monitoring andfire prevention, pollution checks and industrial chemistry applications.Examines their technical development (miniaturisation) and current research;discusses the application of microelectronics and fibre optics. 9 figs.</TEXT></DOC>